Can you use this html code framework and insert the markdown text listed below? I'll divide the sections so you know which is which.

Code framework

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "Inconsolata", monospace;
            font-weight: 400;
            background-color: #000; /* Set your desired background color */
        }
        .intro-text {
            font-family: "Inconsolata", monospace;
            font-size: 17px;
            line-height: 24px;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: white;
        }
        a {
            font-family: "Inconsolata", monospace;
            font-size: 17px;
            line-height: 24px;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: underline; /* Add underline to links */
        }
        h2 {
            font-family: "Inconsolata", monospace;
            color: white;
            font-size: 40px;
            line-height: 44px;
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-bottom: 15px; /* 15px margin below the headers */
        }
    </style>
</head>
